      "side": 1,
      "message": "I find it confusing that the calls to glFlush() and glFinish() are no longer in the finishFlush function.\n\nIt looks to me like the other function is concerned with setting finish callbacks; maybe it could be named appendFinishCallback or addFinishCallback or something? Then this one could remain onFinishFlush().",
